{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.1","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:1","prev_osis_id":"Jer.035.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le livre des proph\u00e9ties de J\u00e9r\u00e9mie br\u00fbl\u00e9 par le roi Jojakim<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-19: cf. 2 Ch 34:14, etc. \u00c9s 58:1-9.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La quatri\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de Jojakim, fils de Josias, roi de Juda, cette parole fut adress\u00e9e \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie de la part de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en ces mots:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.35.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 35:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.35.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.2","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:2","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Prends un livre, et tu y \u00e9criras toutes les paroles que je t\u2019ai dites sur Isra\u00ebl et sur Juda, et sur toutes les nations, depuis le jour o\u00f9 je t\u2019ai parl\u00e9, au temps de Josias, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.3","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:3","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Quand la maison de Juda entendra tout le mal que je pense lui faire, peut-\u00eatre reviendront-ils chacun de leur mauvaise voie; alors je pardonnerai leur iniquit\u00e9 et leur p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.4","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:4","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie appela Baruc, fils de N\u00e9rija; et Baruc \u00e9crivit dans un livre, sous la dict\u00e9e de J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, toutes les paroles que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dites \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.5","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:5","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Puis J\u00e9r\u00e9mie donna cet ordre \u00e0 Baruc: Je suis retenu, et je ne peux pas aller \u00e0 la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.6","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:6","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Tu iras toi-m\u00eame, et tu liras dans le livre que tu as \u00e9crit sous ma dict\u00e9e les paroles de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, aux oreilles du peuple, dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le jour du je\u00fbne; tu les liras aussi aux oreilles de tous ceux de Juda qui seront venus de leurs villes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.7","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:7","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Peut-\u00eatre l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9coutera-t-il leurs supplications, et reviendront-ils chacun de leur mauvaise voie; car grande est la col\u00e8re, la fureur dont l\u2019\u00c9ternel a menac\u00e9 ce peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.8","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:8","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Baruc, fils de N\u00e9rija, fit tout ce que lui avait ordonn\u00e9 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, le proph\u00e8te, et lut dans le livre les paroles de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.9","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:9","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>La cinqui\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de Jojakim, fils de Josias, roi de Juda, le neuvi\u00e8me mois, on publia un je\u00fbne devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel pour tout le peuple de J\u00e9rusalem et pour tout le peuple venu des villes de Juda \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.10","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:10","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Et Baruc lut dans le livre les paroles de J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, aux oreilles de tout le peuple, dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, dans la chambre de Guemaria, fils de Schaphan, le secr\u00e9taire, dans le parvis sup\u00e9rieur, \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la porte neuve de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.11","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:11","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Mich\u00e9e, fils de Guemaria, fils de Schaphan, ayant entendu toutes les paroles de l\u2019\u00c9ternel contenues dans le livre,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.12","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:12","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>descendit \u00e0 la maison du roi, dans la chambre du secr\u00e9taire, o\u00f9 \u00e9taient assis tous les chefs, \u00c9lischama, le secr\u00e9taire, Delaja, fils de Schemaeja, Elnathan, fils d\u2019Acbor, Guemaria, fils de Schaphan, S\u00e9d\u00e9cias, fils de Hanania, et tous les autres chefs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.13","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:13","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et Mich\u00e9e leur rapporta toutes les paroles qu\u2019il avait entendues, lorsque Baruc lisait dans le livre, aux oreilles du peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.14","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:14","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Alors tous les chefs envoy\u00e8rent vers Baruc Jehudi, fils de Nethania, fils de Sch\u00e9l\u00e9mia, fils de Cuschi, pour lui dire: Prends en main le livre dans lequel tu as lu, aux oreilles du peuple, et viens! Baruc, fils de N\u00e9rija, prit en main le livre, et se rendit aupr\u00e8s d\u2019eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.15","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:15","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ils lui dirent: Assieds-toi, et lis-le \u00e0 nos oreilles. Et Baruc lut \u00e0 leurs oreilles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.16","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:16","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils eurent entendu toutes les paroles, ils se regard\u00e8rent avec effroi les uns les autres, et ils dirent \u00e0 Baruc: Nous rapporterons au roi toutes ces paroles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.17","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.17","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:17","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ils pos\u00e8rent encore \u00e0 Baruc cette question: Dis-nous comment tu as \u00e9crit toutes ces paroles sous sa dict\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.18","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:18","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Baruc leur r\u00e9pondit: Il m\u2019a dict\u00e9 de sa bouche toutes ces paroles, et je les ai \u00e9crites dans ce livre avec de l\u2019encre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.17","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.19","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:19","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Les chefs dirent \u00e0 Baruc: Va, cache-toi, ainsi que J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, et que personne ne sache o\u00f9 vous \u00eates.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.20","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.20","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:20","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-32: cf. (J\u00e9 26; 22:13-19.) \u00c9s 30:8-14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Ils all\u00e8rent ensuite vers le roi dans la cour, laissant le livre dans la chambre d\u2019\u00c9lischama, le secr\u00e9taire, et ils en rapport\u00e8rent toutes les paroles aux oreilles du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.21","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:21","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Le roi envoya Jehudi pour prendre le livre, Jehudi le prit dans la chambre d\u2019\u00c9lischama, le secr\u00e9taire, et il le lut aux oreilles du roi et aux oreilles de tous les chefs qui \u00e9taient aupr\u00e8s du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.22","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.20","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.22","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:22","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Le roi \u00e9tait assis dans la maison d\u2019hiver, c\u2019\u00e9tait au neuvi\u00e8me mois, et un brasier \u00e9tait allum\u00e9 devant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.23","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.23","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:23","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Lorsque Jehudi eut lu trois ou quatre feuilles, le roi coupa le livre avec le canif du secr\u00e9taire, et le jeta dans le feu du brasier, o\u00f9 il fut enti\u00e8rement consum\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.24","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.22","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.24","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:24","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Le roi et tous ses serviteurs, qui entendirent toutes ces paroles, ne furent point effray\u00e9s et ne d\u00e9chir\u00e8rent point leurs v\u00eatements.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.25","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.23","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.25","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:25","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Elnathan, Delaja et Guemaria, avaient fait des instances aupr\u00e8s du roi pour qu\u2019il ne br\u00fbl\u00e2t pas le livre; mais il ne les \u00e9couta pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.26","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.24","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.26","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:26","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le roi ordonna \u00e0 Jerachmeel, fils du roi, \u00e0 Seraja, fils d\u2019Azriel, et \u00e0 Sch\u00e9l\u00e9mia, fils d\u2019Abdeel, de saisir Baruc, le secr\u00e9taire, et J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, le proph\u00e8te. Mais l\u2019\u00c9ternel les cacha.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.27","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.25","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.27","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:27","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.028,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Sentence contre le roi.<\/h3>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut adress\u00e9e \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, en ces mots, apr\u00e8s que le roi eut br\u00fbl\u00e9 le livre contenant les paroles que Baruc avait \u00e9crites sous la dict\u00e9e de J\u00e9r\u00e9mie:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.28","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.26","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.28","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:28","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Prends de nouveau un autre livre, et tu y \u00e9criras toutes les paroles qui \u00e9taient dans le premier livre qu\u2019a br\u00fbl\u00e9 Jojakim, roi de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.29","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.27","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.29","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:29","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Et sur Jojakim, roi de Juda, tu diras: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Tu as br\u00fbl\u00e9 ce livre, en disant: Pourquoi y as-tu \u00e9crit ces paroles: Le roi de Babylone viendra, il d\u00e9truira ce pays, et il en fera dispara\u00eetre les hommes et les b\u00eates?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.30","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:30","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.28","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.30","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:30","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel sur Jojakim, roi de Juda: Aucun des siens ne sera assis sur le tr\u00f4ne de David, et son cadavre sera expos\u00e9 \u00e0 la chaleur pendant le jour et au froid pendant la nuit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.31","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:31","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.29","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:29","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.31","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:31","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.036.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Je le ch\u00e2tierai, lui, sa post\u00e9rit\u00e9, et ses serviteurs, \u00e0 cause de leur iniquit\u00e9, et je ferai venir sur eux, sur les habitants de J\u00e9rusalem et sur les hommes de Juda tous les malheurs dont je les ai menac\u00e9s, sans qu\u2019ils aient voulu m\u2019\u00e9couter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.32","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:32","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.30","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:30","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.32","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:32","prev_osis_id":"Jer.036.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.037.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.36.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie prit un autre livre, et le donna \u00e0 Baruc, fils de N\u00e9rija, le secr\u00e9taire. Baruc y \u00e9crivit, sous la dict\u00e9e de J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, toutes les paroles du livre qu\u2019avait br\u00fbl\u00e9 au feu Jojakim, roi de Juda. Beaucoup d\u2019autres paroles semblables y furent encore ajout\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.36","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.37.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 37:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.37.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.36.31","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 36:31","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.36.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb6558847.47296125');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6558847.47296125\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb6558847.47296125","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb6558847.47296125'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6558847.47296125\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}